  "details": "A security flaw has been discovered in OFCMS up to 1.1.3. The impacted element is the function Query of the file ofcms-admin\\src\\main\\java\\com\\ofsoft\\cms\\admin\\controller\\ComnController.java of the component ComnController. Performing a manipulation of the argument system.user.query results in sql injection. The attack may be initiated remotely. The exploit has been released to the public and may be used for attacks. The project was informed of the problem early through an issue report but has not responded yet.",
